---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |TEMP TABLE TRANSFORMATION      |                      |1       |768         |
|1 |├─TEMP TABLE INSERT            |TEMP1                 |0       |762         |
|2 |│ └─MERGE JOIN                 |                      |72      |759         |
|3 |│   ├─TABLE FULL SCAN          |time_dim              |800     |67          |
|4 |│   └─SORT                     |                      |72      |622         |
