|6 |│       ├─TABLE FULL SCAN      |household_demographics|100     |15          |
|7 |│       └─HASH JOIN            |                      |193     |559         |
|8 |│         ├─TABLE FULL SCAN    |web_page              |4       |5           |
|9 |│         └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |web_sales             |3500    |255         |
|10|└─LIMIT                        |                      |1       |7           |
|11|  └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN CARTESIAN |                      |1       |7           |
|12|    ├─SUBPLAN SCAN             |at                    |1       |3           |
|13|    │ └─SCALAR GROUP BY        |                      |1       |3           |
|14|    │   └─TEMP TABLE ACCESS    |VIEW1(TEMP1)          |72      |2           |
|15|    └─SUBPLAN SCAN             |pt                    |1       |3           |
